449
00:30:38,263 --> 00:30:39,349
<i>Salut, Chandra.</i>

450
00:30:39,951 --> 00:30:41,508
<i>Pourquoi refusez-vous
de me parler ?</i>

451
00:30:41,804 --> 00:30:43,413
